# Oversized regenerable firmware-diff files (each exceeds GitHub's 100MB/file limit).
# These can never be pushed. The small *_analysis.md reports are NOT ignored,
# so you can `git add` them normally once they're ready.
# artifacts/firmware_diff/*/report.json
# artifacts/firmware_diff/*/diff/
# artifacts/firmware_diff/*/entitlements/